parameters: \n<Thief A>"Hah, hah... Damn, you've finally given in!"
\n<Thief B>"Hey, the other one's missing! Where did you hide her?!"
\n<Thief A>"What's the matter, you wanna fight? That's pretty funny!"

\n<Deorc>"--Stop it, you guys. What am I supposed to do if she gets
hurt?"
\n<??>"Yeah, that's the sister. Ameria. She's definitely the one."

\n<Ameria>"...You're the leader of the thieves? Why on earth are you
targeting that child... No, why are you targeting us?!"

\n<Deorc>"There's a hefty price on your body. Handing you over will
make for a nice profit... Right, Mr. Riolauno?"

\n<Riolauno>"Sorry, but you're already my valuable merchandise. As a
slave trader, it would tarnish my reputation if anything
happened to you. Don't make a fuss, alright?"

\n<Ameria>"Slave trader? Why me...--! Don't tell me you plan to
capture that child for the same reason?"
\n<Ameria>"...Then I won't let you go any further!"
Ameria readied herself with her weapon in hand.

\n<Deorc>"Whoa... Scary, scary. Being too spirited can also be a
hassle."

\n<Deorc>"...Sister. Like I said before, I don't want to hurt you.
Can't you just quietly do as you're told?"
\n<Ameria>"Who would listen to what you say?!"

\n<Deorc>"Heh heh... Listen up, Sister. The reason this village is in
such a mess is all because of you lot."

\n<Deorc>"That means, what we do to this village from now on depends
on your attitude."

\n<Deorc>"If you quietly comply, we'll just take the booze and
valuables and won't do anything more."

\n<Deorc>"But if you refuse... Well, we might have to make someone in
this village suffer, right?"

\n<Deorc>"And there's one more thing. About the woman who fled with
you."

\n<Deorc>"We've got orders for her too... It's not kidnapping. It's
'murder'."

\n<Deorc>"She's still hiding nearby, isn't she?... If we set fire to
the village, we could save the trouble of searching and kill
her too, maybe?"

\n<Deorc>"Heh heh. If you want us to stop... You know what to do,
Sister."
\n<Ameria>"...I'll do as you say, so please don't harm anyone else."

\n<Deorc>"Hey, don't let her escape. And don't put any scratches on
her."

\n<Deorc>"Alright. You lot, find the other woman! Once you find her,
you can kill her!"

\n<Ameria>"Wait! I did as you asked, so don't lay a hand on that
child!"

\n<Deorc>"What are you talking about? No matter what you do, killing
that woman isn't going to change. It's just business."

\n<Deorc>"If you don't listen, I'll really set the place on fire.
Just shut up and follow me!"
